#: froide/foirequest/templates/foirequest/emails/became_asleep.txt:1
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"Your request “%(title)s” is not marked as resolved and has not seen any "
"activity in the last 6 months. Therefore your request has been marked "
"asleep.\n"
"\n"
"If you received a postal answer, please upload it to the request:\n"
"\n"
"%(upload_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"If you have not received an answer, you can send a reminder to the public "
"body:\n"
"\n"
"%(write_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"If you are no longer interested in the request, you can mark it as resolved "
"here:\n"
"\n"
"%(status_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Cheers,\n"
"%(site_name)s"
msgstr ""
"Hallo %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"Ihre Anfrage „%(title)s“ hat kein Ergebnis und hatte in den letzten 6 "
"Monaten keine Aktivität. Daher ist Ihre Anfrage jetzt eingeschlafen.\n"
"Falls Sie in der Zwischenzeit eine Antwort per Post erhalten haben, laden "
"Sie diese bitte hoch:\n"
"\n"
"%(upload_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Falls Sie keine Antwort erhalten haben, können Sie der Behörde eine "
"Erinnerung schicken:\n"
"\n"
"%(write_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Falls Sie kein Interesse mehr an der Anfrage haben, können Sie die Anfrage "
"einfach als abgeschlossen markieren:\n"
"\n"
"%(status_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Beste Grüße,\n"
"%(site_name)s"

#: froide/foirequest/templates/foirequest/emails/became_overdue.txt:1
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"Your request “%(title)s” seems to not have gotten an answer in the required "
"time and became overdue.\n"
"We recommend that you send another message to the public body to check the "
"status of the request and if they received it.\n"
"\n"
"%(write_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"If you received a postal answer, please upload it to the request:\n"
"\n"
"%(upload_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"If you are no longer interested in the request, you can set its status to "
"resolved:\n"
"\n"
"%(status_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Cheers,\n"
"%(site_name)s"
msgstr ""
"Hallo %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"Ihre Anfrage „%(title)s“ wurde offenbar nicht in der gesetzlichen Frist "
"beantwortet und ist nun verspätet.\n"
"Wir empfehlen Ihnen eine weitere Nachricht an die Behörde zu senden und den "
"Status der Anfrage zu erfragen.\n"
"\n"
"%(write_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Falls Sie zwischenzeitlich eine Antwort per Post erhalten haben, fügen Sie "
"diese Antwort bitte Ihrer Anfrage hinzu.\n"
"Hier ist ein Link zu Ihrer Anfrage:\n"
"\n"
"%(upload_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Falls Sie kein Interesse mehr an der Anfrage haben, können Sie die Anfrage "
"einfach als abgeschlossen markieren:\n"
"\n"
"%(status_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Beste Grüße,\n"
"%(site_name)s"

#: froide/foirequest/templates/foirequest/emails/classification_reminder.txt:1
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"Your request \"%(title)s\" has received a reply, but it is unclear if the "
"request is now finished.\n"
"\n"
"Please use the following link to set if the request is still ongoing or "
"finished:\n"
"%(status_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Cheers,\n"
"%(site_name)s"
msgstr ""
"Hallo %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"Ihre Anfrage „%(title)s“ hat zwar bereits eine Antwort erhalten, aber es ist "
"unklar, ob die Anfrage damit abgeschlossen ist.\n"
"\n"
"Bitte stellen Sie unter folgendem Link ein, ob die Anfrage noch läuft oder "
"abgeschlossen ist:\n"
"%(status_action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Beste Grüße,\n"
"%(site_name)s"

#: froide/foirequest/templates/foirequest/emails/confirm_foi_message_sent.txt:1
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"your message for the Freedom of Information request \"%(title)s\" has been "
"sent to %(pbname)s. We will notify you when you get a response.\n"
"\n"
"%(action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Cheers,\n"
"%(site_name)s\n"
msgstr ""
"Hallo %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"Ihre Nachricht zur Anfrage „%(title)s“ an %(pbname)s wurde gesendet. Wir "
"werden Sie benachrichtigen, sobald Sie eine Antwort erhalten.\n"
"\n"
"%(action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Beste Grüße,\n"
"%(site_name)s\n"

#: froide/foirequest/templates/foirequest/emails/confirm_foi_project_created.txt:1
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"your project \"%(title)s\" has been created and we are sending the requests "
"to the public bodies now. We will notify you when you get responses.\n"
"\n"
"%(action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Cheers,\n"
"%(site_name)s\n"
msgstr ""
"Hallo %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"Ihr Projekt „%(title)s“ wurde erstellt und wir versenden gerade Ihre "
"Anfragen an die Behörden. Wir werden Sie benachrichtigen, sobald Sie "
"Antworten erhalten.\n"
"\n"
"%(action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Beste Grüße\n"
"%(site_name)s\n"

#: froide/foirequest/templates/foirequest/emails/confirm_foi_request_sent.txt:1
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"your request \"%(title)s\" to \"%(public_body)s\" has been sent. We will "
"notify you when you get a response.\n"
"\n"
"%(action_url)s\n"
"\n"
"Cheers,\n"
"%(site_name)s\n"
msgstr ""
"Hallo %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"Ihre Anfrage „%(title)s“ an %(public_body)s wurde gesendet. Wir werden Sie "
